        <div class="assignment-details-summary">
          <p><span class="assignment-text-lead">SUMMARY</span> College participants take inventory of their assets. They explore their passions in life and potential professional career interests that align with their assets and market place contexts. They also discuss ways to identify purposeful and fulfilling summer opportunities and position themselves on paths geared toward longer term success.
          </p>
        </div>
